<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>pūmaruviya ticaimukattoṉ paṭaitta perumpuvi viḷaṅka temaruviya pacuntuḷavattiru neṭu<unclear>mā</unclear> livaneṉna 
<lb n="2"/><unclear>va</unclear>raiyāḻi neṭumpuṟattuḷorāḻi taṉi naṭātti Uṭaiya kulattavatarittuk karuṅkaliyiṉniruḷotuṅkak katir veṇku<unclear>ṭ</unclear>ai nilāveṟippa varuṅkatirin veyil
<lb n="3"/>virikkum maṇimakuṭam puṉaintaruḷi maṇkaḷippavum maṉaṅkaḷippavu malar maṭantaiyan mutal maṅkaiyar kaṇkaḷippavun taṇṇaḷip peruṅkaruṇaiyāl mutaṟkāval pūṇ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭu cempon viraciṅṅācaṉattup puvaṉamuḻutuṭaiyāḷoṭum viṟṟiruntaruḷiya koirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ri<hi rend="grantha">panma</hi>rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi><note n="21-1">Incomplete.</note>
</p>

